Package: r4c
Title: Range Condition Classification and Carrying Capacity Tools
Version: 0.1-1
Author: Mansour Mesdaghi [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Mansour Mesdaghi <mmesdagh@yahoo.com>
Authors@R:
    person("Mansour", "Mesdaghi", email = "mmesdagh@yahoo.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools for range condition classification using a six-factor scoring
    workflow and for carrying capacity estimation using comparative yield and
    double sampling methods. The package accepts either Excel workbooks or
    in-memory data frames and returns structured results for operational use.
License: GPL (>= 3)
